@Manuals_HostAddress = http://localhost:5053
@conversationId = conv-001

### POST chat — first turn with system prompt
POST {{Manuals_HostAddress}}/api/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "conversationId": "{{conversationId}}",
  "message": "What is the capital of France?",
  "systemPrompt": "You are a concise assistant. Answer in one sentence."
}

###

### POST chat — second turn (history maintained, no systemPrompt needed)
POST {{Manuals_HostAddress}}/api/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "conversationId": "{{conversationId}}",
  "message": "What language do they speak there?"
}

###

### DELETE — clear conversation history
DELETE {{Manuals_HostAddress}}/api/chat/{{conversationId}}

###

### OpenAPI spec (development only)
GET {{Manuals_HostAddress}}/openapi/v1.json

###
